OL,3,CShortage of BSL interpreters 'putting
OL,4,Cnew law's success in doubt'
OL,6,FStephen has echoed the concerns raised
OL,7,Fby the Senedd' Equality and Social
OL,8,FJustice Committee about the lack of
OL,9,FBSL interpreters in Wales.
OL,11,F"The problems we face as interpreters
OL,12,Fand translators is that there's a
OL,13,Fnational shortage, and it's even worse
OL,14,Fin Wales," he said. "Of the number of
OL,15,Finterpreters and translators in the
OL,16,FUK, only 4% of those are living and
OL,17,Fworking in Wales."
