OL,3,CShortage of BSL interpreters 'putting
OL,4,Cnew law's success in doubt'
OL,6,FStephen believes the Bill could make
OL,7,Fthe situation even worse in Wales,
OL,8,Fwithout proper training routes opened
OL,9,Fup.
OL,11,F"There's no training for interpreters
OL,12,Fin Wales, if you want to be trained to
OL,13,Fbe an interpreter or translator you
OL,14,Fhave to go to England. There is
OL,15,Fnothing in Wales at all."
OL,17,FJenny Rathbone MS, who chairs the
OL,18,FEquality and Social Justice Committee,
OL,19,Fshares many of Stephen's concerns.
