OL,3,CShortage of BSL interpreters 'putting
OL,4,Cnew law's success in doubt'
OL,6,F"The shortage of interpreters and
OL,7,Ftranslators in Wales stands out as the
OL,8,Fgreatest threat to the success of this
OL,9,Fproposed law," the Welsh Labour MS
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"The current interpreter workforce is
OL,13,Ftoo small as some interpreters are due
OL,14,Fto retire, while demand is set to rise
OL,15,Fsignificantly.
OL,17,F"Unless urgent and sustained action is
OL,18,Ftaken to address this shortfall, there
OL,19,Fis a real risk that Deaf BSL signers
OL,20,Fwill continue to face unacceptable
OL,21,Fbarriers."
