OL,6,FAlthough the Senedd committee said
OL,7,Fimmediate and sustained investment in
OL,8,Finterpreter and translator training,
OL,9,Frecruitment, and retention is needed,
OL,10,Fit concluded that if the Bill is
OL,11,Fdelivered rigorously it could bring
OL,12,F"real and lasting change".
